textAnnotations.description:
You, or your loved ones with vision impairment will be able to:
• Scan and read the fine print on medical
prescriptions
• Read the legal documents
• Enjoy a little bit of freedom, self-
sufficiency and dignity
My grandpa is almost 90 years old and lives alone. He is a very
proud person and it is embarassing for him to ask me to read him
the fine print on the letters, documents and prescription he gets.
Sometimes, he feels very upset that he has to wait for me to
read it for him.
I built this app for him, so he can roam around and feel in
control.
